substep.ask:
PR review cycle complete after {{iteration_count}} iterations. All Gemini feedback addressed, declined, or deferred. The PR is ready for your merge decision.
Summary: {{escalation_summary}}
Merge the PR? - Merge with squash (Recommended): I'll run `gh pr merge --squash --delete-branch`, then run `wt remove {{branch}}`. - Merge with rebase: I'll run `gh pr merge --rebase --delete-branch`, then run `wt remove {{branch}}`. - Merge with merge commit: I'll run `gh pr merge --merge --delete-branch`, then run `wt remove {{branch}}`. - Hold: don't merge yet; I want to inspect the PR myself first.
